[src:static-site-generation/elements-template] First the code gets the slots within the shadow root, then the text to be inserted, and finally assigns the text to the slot.
[src:static-site-generation/elements-template] Note that you can only assign a node once to any particular slot, and that if you assign multiple nodes to a single slot using `HTMLSlotElement.assign()`, the order they are specified controls the order they are added.
